title: 【mythicmobs】为什么伪装没用
author: 何昌浩
txt_content:
各位带师兄，咱这mobs的怪物伪装无用请各位带佬康康：
  Disguise:
    Type: player
    Player: '&bLv.1&a普通哥布林'
    Skin: Goblin

这东西只显示player没有皮肤skin

replies.author: 名副其实
replies.txt_content:
请在主楼补充编辑！
另外mm似乎对大小写敏感
请将伪装生物名称改为大写

replies.author: 叽叽小石头
replies.txt_content:
https://www.spigotmc.org/wiki/lib-s-disguises/

These are direct links to old, unsupported versions of Lib's Disguises.

8.2.6 (1.7)
8.6.8 (1.8) or 8.6.7 (1.8)
9.0.6 (1.9)
9.5.2 (1.12.2)(or an experimental 9.5.2 (1.12.2)) which requires ProtocolLib 4.3.0
9.8.2 (1.13.2) which requires ProtocolLib 4.4.0
9.8.4 (1.14.4) which requires ProtocolLib 4.5.0 Gradle


1.15.2用最新版https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/libs-disguises.32453/
